Files and Directories:

libraries - the libraries directory contains the library to
communicate via the Anaconda shield with a Linksprite wifi module.

linksprite_setup - the linksprite_setup directory contains an example
that shows how to set and read parameters from the Linksprite module

linksprite_scanning - the linksprite_scanning directory contains an example
that scans for AP stations and prints them to a serial port

linksprite_rxtx - the linksprite_rxtx directory contains an example
that sends packets

udpServer.java - A small Java server script (other programs, like
netcat, etc. can be used too of course)
